┴A GOOD NAME IS RATHER TO BE CHOSEN THAN GREAT RICHES AND LOVING FAVOUR RATHER THAN SILVER AND GOLD
PROVERBS 22 CHAPTER 1

THANKS BE TO GOD
FOR THE SACRED REMEMBRANCE OF
MY BELOVED HUSBAND
SIDNEY JOHN FIELD
A FRIEND OF NORTON LINDSEY
AND A LOVER OF THE
SURROUNDING COUNTRY
TO KEEP HIS MEMORY GREEN
FEBRUARY 1934"╦
╚This bench has been funded by donations
from staff in the Finance Office
and across the University in fond memory
of Rachel Brown and former colleagues.
Always in our thoughts and never forgotten."Ņ
ļIN LOVING MEMORY OF
JAMES AND ESTHER GRANT

In Loving Memory of
JANET WILD
Fell Asleep on 22nd February 2015
Much loved Wife, Mother, Sister, Grandma,
